Final Rule Generation
Once the CEL path is generated, it can be combined with the rule template.Example template:
has(message.%s) && double(message.%s) < %s
For array fields, the condition should be applied to the iterator field:
message.Header.SystemIdentification.all(x,has(x.Identification.Scheme.COLUMN_LONG_1) &&double(x.Identification.Scheme.COLUMN_LONG_1) < 100)
This ensures the rule is evaluated for every element in the array.
